phpDocumentor2
==============

phpDocumentor2 is a natural evolution from phpDocumentor (http://phpdoc.org) which was written long ago and has since become an unmaintainable mess.

Development
-----------

phpDocumentor2 is currently unusable as Development has not yet reached an alpha stage.  If you wish to help, please feel free to fork and contribute.

Dependencies
------------
phpDocumentor2 is dependant upon the following Pear2 projects:

* [PEAR2_Autoload](http://pear2.php.net/PEAR2_Autoload)
* [PEAR2_Console_CommandLine](http://pear2.php.net/PEAR2_Console_CommandLine)
* [PEAR2_Exception](http://pear2.php.net/PEAR2_Exception)
